Constructor:
a special block of code to initialize the fields/properties of a class

default constructor assign a defaoult values:
    int number; //0
    boolean flag; //false
    String str; //null
    double db;  //0.0
    car ch;   //ghost latter (nothing is diplayed
---------
to create a default constructor
for instance:
class ABC{
